ite]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Centre left]] to [[left wing]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA||row}}\n| Canada's Fourth Front\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2019\n| \n| Partap Dua\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA||row}}\n| [[Canadian Nationalist Party]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2017\n| [[Canadian nationalism]], [[white nationalism]]\n| Travis Patron\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Far right]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|Christian Heritage|row}}\n| [[Christian Heritage Party of Canada]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti de l'H\u00e9ritage Chr\u00e9tien du Canada}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1986\n| [[Social conservatism]], [[Christian right]]\n| Rodney L. Taylor\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Right wing]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|Communist|row}}\n| [[Communist Party of Canada]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti communiste du Canada}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1921\n| [[Communism]], [[Marxist-Leninism]]\n| [[Liz Rowley]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 3 (1945)<ref>Includes members using temporary party names [[Unity (Canada)|Unity]] and [[Labor-Progressive Party]].</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| {{sort|1.2%|1% (1945)}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Left wing]] to [[far left]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|Libertarian|row}}\n| [[Libertarian Party of Canada]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti Libertarien du Canada}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1973\n| [[Libertarianism]]\n| [[Tim Moen]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 